            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                这些节点对网络的健康而言十分重要，它们能让客户端同步和通过全网快速广播信息。我们提议增加次级网络，名为达世主节点网络。这些节点将具有高可用性，而且在为网络提供符合一定要求的服务后能够得到主节点服务奖励。。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.1 主节点奖励计划——成本和奖励
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                比特币网络全节点锐减的主要原因是缺乏对运行节点的奖励。随着时间的推移，全网接入的用户会更多，对带宽的需求会更高，对节点运行者的资金需求也更多，结果使运行全节点的成本提高。考虑到成本的上升，节点运行者必须要降低他们的运行成本或者运行轻客户端，但这样完全不利于网络健康。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
