            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                运行一个主节点，需要存储1000DASH。当主节点生效时，它可为全网的客户端提供服务，并以利息的形式获取奖励。这就使得用户为这项服务投资，但同时得到一定的回报。主节点获取的收益是来自同一个矿池，大约有45%的区块奖励纳入到这个计划中。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                考虑到主节点奖励计划的奖励率是固定的百分比，还有主节点网络节点存在波动的事实，预计主节点奖励会根据当前生效的主节点总数作出变化。通过以下的计算公式可计算出运行主节点一整天的收益：
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">(n/t) * r * b * a</strong>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                n: 运行者控制的主节点数
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                t: 主节点的总数
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                r: 当前的区块奖励（当前平均奖励是5DASH）
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                b: 平均每天的区块数，当前DASH网络每天区块通常是576个
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                a: 主节点的平均奖励（平均每个区块奖励的45%）
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                运行主节点的收益公式：<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">((n/t) * r * b * a * 365) / 1000</strong>（式子中的变量与上述相同）
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                运行主节点需要成本，这在网络上创建了生效节点的硬限制和软限制。目前有530万DASH流通，只有5300个节点可能可以在网络上运行。软限制由配置节点所花的成本和平台的滞留量所致，因为DASH是流通的货币，而不仅仅是为投资所用。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.2 确定顺序
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                使用特定的确定算法创建主节点的伪随机排序。使用为每个区块设计的工作量证明机制的哈希算法，挖矿网络可以提供支持这个排序的安全性。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                选择主节点的代码：
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="314" width="726" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPoj9JIdXBVss8pFeSrhUVMUDYGKUdttkOLrIDto1meEzxK0azmCynBXg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                示例代码还可以进一步扩展为主节点排序，“第二”，“第三”和“第四”个主节点的计算依此类推。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.3 非信任制的Quorum
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                当前 DASH 网络大约具有2400个生效的主节点，而需要1000 DASH担保才可成为一个生效的主节点。我们创建了一个系统，其中没有一人能控制整个主节点网络。例如，如果有人想控制50％的主节点网络，他们将不得不从公开市场上购买230万个DASH。这将极大提高币价，所以获得如此多DASH是不可能的。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在拥有主节点网络和担保条件的前提下，我们以非信任制的方式使用该次级网络进行高度敏感的任务，其中没人能控制网络的演变结果。从总池中选择N个伪随机主节点来执行相同的任务，这些节点可以充当裁判，过程无需整个网络的参与。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                例如，一个非信任制的Quorum发现InstantX，InstantX会使用Quorum确认交易和锁定输入。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                另一个例子是，非信任制的Quorum可以利用主节点网络作为金融市场的去中心化预言者，这让实现去中心化的合同成为可能。例如苹果公司的股价在2016年12月31日超过300美元的话，就提交公约A，否则提交公约B。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.4 角色和服务量证明机制
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                主节点可以向网络提供任意的额外服务。正如在概念中指出，我们的首个成功应用是 Darksend（匿名发送）和 InstantX（即时支付）。使用我们称之为“服务量证明”的机制，可以要求这些节点处于在线状态，即使在正确的区块高度上也要作出响应。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                恶意者也可以运行主节点，但不会对网络提供任何实质性的服务。为了减少这些人使用系统做出对自己节点有利事情的概率，必须ping剩余网络以确保它们保持活跃。这项工作通过主节点网络在每个区块选择2个Quorum来完成。Quorum A检查Quorum B每个区块的服务。Quorum A是与当前区块哈希最接近的节点，而Quorum B是远离所说区块哈希最远的节点。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                主节点A（1）检查主节点B（2300）<br/>主节点A（2）检查主节点B（2299）<br/>主节点A（3）检查主节点B（2298）
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                检查网络就是要验证节点是生效的，这由主节点自身完成。全网区块的1％会受到检查。这使整个网络在一天中会被检查大约6次。为了保持这个系统是非信任制的，我们使用Quorum系统中随机选择节点，但我们最少也需要六次检查来排查一个恶意节点。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                为达到欺骗系统的目的，攻击者需要在一轮中被选中六次。否则，欺骗的目的就被系统发现，使其不会得逞，其它节点也是这样。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="253" width="932" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPoTC3icxgNktEK9yeTZzYBun7cPiaiadvu5NLCdBYeakP1ia0uc03RVaAVfg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                表1 在服务性证明机制失衡的情况下，一个独立的主节点欺骗系统的概率
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                n:攻击者控制的主节点数<br/>t:全网主节点总数<br/>r:区块链深度<br/>基于Quorum系统，主节点的选择是伪随机的。&nbsp;
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.5 主节点协议
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                主节点使用一系列扩展协议在全网进行广播，包括主节点消息announce机制和主节点消息ping机制。这两类机制用来确认全网节点处于生效状态，除了它们，执行服务量证明机制需求的还有Darksend和InstantX。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在钱包中发送1000DASH到特定地址，就激活代码自然生成能在全网进行广播的主节点， 随之次级私钥生成，它是用来对其它所有信息进行签名，另外在运行单机模式时还可用来完全锁定钱包。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在两台独立的机器上使用次级私钥让冷模式成为可能。主要的“热”客户端对1000 DASH的输入进行签名，此过程包含使用二级私钥对信息进行签名。 之后，“冷”客户端能发现包含次级私钥的信息并将主节点激活。这让“热”客户端失效（客户端关闭），这样攻击者访问激活后的主节点也不可能获得窃取其中的1000DASH。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                主节点开始运行时，会向全网发送“主节点广播”信息，
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                包含有：
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                信息：（1000DASH输入，可访问的IP地址，签名，签名时间，含有1000Dash的公钥，次级公钥，用于捐赠的公钥，捐赠的百分比）
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                此后每隔15分钟，一条ping信息会对外发送，证明节点生效中。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                信息：（1000DASH的输入，签名（使用次级私钥），签名时间）
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                随着时间的推移，网络会移除失效的节点，让该节点不再被客户端利用或再用于支付。节点也可以不停地ping网络，但如果它们的端口不打开，最终会被标记为失效状态，不再用于支付。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.6主节点列表的广播
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                进入DASH网络的新客户端必须发现当前全网活跃的主节点，这样才可以使用它们的服务。一旦它们加入网状网络，它们的节点就会收到请求主节点列表的指令。设置缓存的目的是让客户端记录主节点及其当前状态，因此当客户端重新启动时，他们只需简单加载该文件，不需重新请求主节点的完整列表。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                2.7使用挖矿进行支付和强制规定
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                为了确保每个主节点都获得应有的区块奖励，网络必须强制每个区块支付奖励给正确的主节点。如果矿工不愿意的话，他们的区块必须被网络拒绝，否则作弊就会产生。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                我们提出一个策略，就是一个主节点代表一个Quorum，选择其中优胜的主节点然后广播它们的信息。信息得到N次广播后，会选择同一目标接收者，这样达成共识后选中的区块要对该主节点支付奖励。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在网上挖矿时，矿池（矿池的作用是将单独的矿工整合起来）使用RPC API接口获取生成有关区块的信息。为了向主节点支付奖励，必须添加次级接收者到GetBlockTemplate来扩展接口。矿池之后广播自己的成功开采的区块，使自己和主节点之间保持同步。
            </p>
            <h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3. 匿名支付
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                我们相信，为了能在客户端提高强度保护用户隐私，实现标准的非信任制是很重要的。例如electrum，Android和iPhone这些客户端，也会直接嵌入相同的匿名层和很好利用协议扩展性。这让用户使用坚实稳固的系统匿名发送资金时有着相同的体验。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                Darksend 是 CoinJoin（提供匿名技术的软件）的改进和扩展版本。除了拥有CoinJoin的核心理念，我们还进行一系列的改进，例如去中心化、使用链接实现强匿名、相同面值和被动先进的混币技术。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在提高隐私和加密数字货币的可互换性时，最大的挑战是，无法做到加密整个区块链。在以比特币为基础的加密数字货币体系内，能看到哪些输出是没发送，哪些是已发送，通常将其称为UTXO，全称是未使用交易输出。这让每个用户在公共帐本中都可充当诚实交易保证者的角色。比特币的协议是在不依赖第三方参与的前提下设计的，没有第三方的参与，仍能通过公共区块链随时读取用户信息实现审计是至关重要的。我们的目标是在不失去这些要素的前提下提高保密性和可互换性，我们坚信这是创建成功数字货币的关键。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                使用数字货币范围内去中心化的混币服务，我们能让货币本身具备完全可互换的能力。可互换性是金钱的属性，决定货币的各单位要保持平等。当你以通货的形式接收资金时，资金不应该保留之前用户的使用记录，或者用户能很轻易地与之前的使用历史撇清开来，从而做到所有货币是平等的。与此同时，任何用户在不影响他人隐私的情况下，保证公共账本的每笔交易都是诚实的。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                为了提高可互换性和保持公共区块链的诚实性，我们提议使用先进的非信任制去中心化混币技术，为了保持通货的可互换性，这项服务直接整合到这个货币体系中，对于每个用户而言都可容易和安全使用。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3.1 Coinjoin通过账户可追踪资金流向
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                一个简单的策略是在现有的比特币基础上整合Coinjoin，就是单纯将交易合并在一起。通过追踪联合交易的用户资金流向就会将用户的身份暴露出来。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                图2：例如将2个用户的交易整合为Coinjoin交易
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在这项交易里，0.05个比特币使用混币技术对外发送，为了追踪这笔资金的来源，仅需要把右边的数额加起来再和左边的数额匹配就可得知。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                重新组合交易
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                0.05+0.0499+0.0001(fee) = 0.10BTC.<br/>0.0499+0.05940182+0.0001(fee) = 0.10940182BTC.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                随着更多用户加入到混币的过程中，获得结果的难度会以指数级增长。然而，在以后某个时间点结果还是可以被追踪出来，匿名性失效。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3.2直接链接和中继链接
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在Coinjoin其它实现的应用里，用户先把资金匿名化，最后把交易发送到知道发送者身份的平台或个体，这点是有可能实现的。但这打破了匿名性，能让其它人往前追踪用户的交易，我们称这类型的攻击为“中继链接”。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="493" width="860" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPoBqB0IP8uZibNxCBbMwWTibXTkiajpjFGtRxy5owuBRRe4icxEaJ21E1TNA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                图3： 中继转换链接
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在这个例子中，Alice匿名发送1.2BTC，分别以1BTC和0.2BTC对外输出，然后从1BTC的输出中再对外输出0.7BTC，剩余0.3BTC，这0.3BTC输出发送到可识别对象去，但实质上Alice已经将0.7BTC成功匿名发送出去。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                为了确定匿名交易的发送者身份，要从“交换交易”环节开始，通过区块链往前追溯，直至找到“Alice匿名发送0.7个BTC”。一旦找到的话，你会发现那是你的用户最近匿名购买了东西，从而看透这个匿名交易。我们称这种类型的攻击为“中介转换链接”。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="497" width="849" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPoIekgS7OrRrdYS9MMXWCicw4md1rBpzfh40RiaUMqYXiaibW9QTZcTBfQFw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                图4：中介转换链接
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在第二个例子中，Alice在coinbase处花费了1.2BTC，然后将这数额匿名化再以1BTC输出。接着，她又花费1BTC，剩余0.3BTC再结合之前的0.2BTC，组成为0.5BTC对外输出。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                结合匿名交易和CoinJoin交易，将前后的整个交易历史整理一遍，从而可彻底看穿这个匿名功能。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3.3增强的隐私和DOS防护
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                多方的交易可以合并为一个交易，Darksend很好地利用了这点，它将多方的资金合并在一起对外发送，这样一旦整合后就无法再次拆分。考虑到Darksend交易是专门为用户支付设置的，这个系统是高度安全防盗窃，用户的货币是十分安全的。目前，使用Darksend的混币技术至少需要3方参与。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="594" width="780" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPox3cfp43V13CbZXXXXUDxbRVIATzNnqctR0yrO84pg5icjpp9RJuhib0w/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                图5：三个用户的资金合并到一个共同交易，用户会以新的打乱过的形式对外输出资金。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                为了从整体上增强系统的隐私性，我们提以使用0.1DASH，1DASH，10DASH和100DASH的相同面值。在每轮混币过程中，所有用户应该以相同面值的形式输入和输出资金。除了使用相同面值外，交易手续费会被移除，而且所有交易会分解成分散的、独立的、前后没有关联的小交易。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                接下是应对可能的DOS攻击，我们提议所有用户在加入时把交易以押金的形式提交到矿池去，交易最后还是输出到用户，同时又可向矿工支付一笔高的报酬。也就是说，用户向混币池提高请求时，交易一开始就要提供押金。如果某个时候用户不合作了，例如拒绝签名，押金交易会自动在全网广播，若要在匿名网络上进行持续攻击，所付出的代价是极其高昂的。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3.4被动的资金和区块链匿名
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                Darksend每轮的混币限制为1000DASH,并多轮混币才能匿名混合相当数量的资金。为了让用户体验方便和攻击变得困难，Darksend以被动的模式运行。同时设定时间间隔，用户的客户端要通过主节点连接其它客户端。一旦进入主节点，用户要求需要匿名的面值数额会在全网依次排队广播，但是没有信息会将用户的身份暴露出来。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                每轮的Darksend过程可视为增强用户资金匿名性的独立事件，然而每轮只限制3个参与者，因此观察者有三分之一的机会追踪交易，为了提高匿名的质量，会采用链接的方法，将资金通过多个主节点依次发送出去。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="159" width="925" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPoBnOhEP8SVicAVXp26BibV6Lwiaco3sqau5Bbyr9fprgY8QsXFk1X881uQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                表2. N轮混币中可能涉及的用户数&nbsp;
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3.5安全性考虑
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                由于交易合并在一起，主节点在用户资金流过时有可能进行“窥探”。由于每个主节点都被要求持有1000 DASH和用户选用随机主节点来部署他们的资金，所以“窥探”的影响性不大。通过区块链追踪交易的概率计算如下所示。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                表3.考虑到攻击者控制N个节点时，在全网追踪Darksend交易的概率
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                n 攻击者控制总的节点数<br/>t：全网主节点总数<br/>r: 区块链深度<br/>主节点的选择是随机的
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                考虑到DASH的有限供应（此时此刻撰写白皮书时有530万个DASH在流通）和市场上低的流动性，在一次攻击中控制如此之多的主节点是不可能的。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                通过遮掩主节点上发生的交易来扩展系统，也会大大提高系统的安全性。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                &nbsp;
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                3.6使用中继系统遮掩主节点
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                &nbsp;
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在3.4一节，我们描述了使用Darksend多轮混币技术追踪单一交易的概率。这可以进一步通过遮掩主节点加以强化，使他们不能看到用户输入/输出方向。要做到这一点，我们提出一个简单的可让用户保护自己的身份的中继系统。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                我们不让用户向矿池直接提交输入和输出的交易，而是让他们从全网随机选择主节点然后要求它将输入/输出/的签名中继传输到目标主节点。这意味着，主节点将接收N次的输入/输出和N组签名。每轮混币只为其中一个用户服务，但主节点无法知道究竟是哪个用户。
            </p>
            <h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                4. 使用InstantX进行即时交易
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                使用主节点的Quorum，用户能够发送和接收即时不可逆转交易。一旦Quorum形成，该交易的输入被锁定到对应的特定交易去，而目前全网交易锁定的时间是大约4秒。如果在主节点网络达成锁定的共识，所有与之冲突的交易和区块将被永远拒绝，除非它们能匹配当时锁定的交易对应ID。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                这将允许商家在现实商业中使用移动设备来替换传统POS机器，用户可像使用传统纸币一样快速进行面对面的非商业交易。这过程是没有中心权威的干预。此功能的广泛综述可以在InstantX白皮书中找到。
            </p>
            <h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                5. 其他改进
            </h2>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                5.1 x11算法
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                X11是一种广泛使用的哈希算法，其与其它算法不同，称为链接运算。 X11由11 轮SHA3算法组成，每轮哈希计算的结果都被提交到区块链的下一轮计算去。使用多轮算法，可以减少专门为数字货币挖矿设计的ASIC使用的概率。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                在比特币的生命周期，在挖矿开始时它的爱好者是使用CPU的，不久之后是使用GPU软件，而GPU快速取代了CPU。几年后属于GPU的周期结束，ASIC即是专用集成电路被研发出来，其也迅速取代了GPU。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                考虑到专门为X11算法而设计的ASIC矿机的复杂性和机器制造的困难性，我们预计这将需要比比特币更多的时间进行研发，这就允许爱好者有更长的时间参与挖矿。我们深信这对均与的分配和数字货币的成长起着极其重要的作用。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                跨链哈希运算的另一个好处是高端的CPU有着跟同级GPU接近的平均回报。GPU消耗的功率已有30-50%的下降，比大多数加密数字货币使用的Scrypt算法的功率少得多。
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                5.2挖矿供应
            </h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                DASH采用另一种可降低挖矿引起的通胀的方法，就是每年的供应进行7%的减产，这不同于其它数字货币的减半。另外，每个区块的供应量与全网的矿工数直接相关，更多矿工的参与意味着更少的挖矿奖励。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                DASH的开取计划会在本世纪持续，慢慢直至到下世纪中叶，最终在2150年左右挖矿才会停止。
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                <img class="" height="742" width="890" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nAXL5v4mpSp0LAaqiaBUiaicmRc1pbADiaPofFyyic2yBrcySnw3HVKo2WZworX6bGb13RUicwmJGQ8PSEaZzef4gibRA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                图6：挖矿奖励模型
            </p>
            <h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.1; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                5. 结论
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
                本白皮书介绍各种旨在提高比特币协议的概念，这对于普通用户来说意味着，有更好的隐私性、可互换性、更少的价格波动和全网更快的信息广播。这一切都是通过使用two-tier激励模型，而不是借用其它数字货币如比特币现有的single-tier模型来实现。使用这个可替代的网络设计让添加更多类型的服务成为可能，例如去中心化的混币技术、即时交易和使用主节点quorum的去中心化预言。
